1
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:00,840
We're here.

2
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,760
Let's go check Siniang's roof.

3
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:11,599
Come on up.

4
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,199
Master Kun.

5
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,479
How am I supposed to get up there?

6
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,759
I don't know martial arts.

7
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,360
How about...

8
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,080
as my good disciple,

9
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,840
you come down and carry me up?

10
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,879
Master Kun, I'm afraid of heights!

11
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,599
I say, can you be a bit gentler?

12
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,000
Look there. Someone moved the tiles.

13
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:52,879
It should be right here.

14
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,639
You mean to say...

15
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:05,319
the killer struck from the roof...

16
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:07,039
to murder Ding Da?

17
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,800
Why have we been called here again?

18
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:22,960
Exactly. Day after day,

19
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:24,639
we haven't even had a peaceful meal.

20
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:26,879
My apologies.

21
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,319
Sorry to keep everyone waiting.

22
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,000
Has the Divine Doctor deciphered the code?

23
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,840
Based on the current clues,

24
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,520
the truth will soon surface.

25
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:37,879
Rest assured.

26
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,240
Has Divine Doctor Du found the killer?

27
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,759
I have found the method the killer used here

28
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,280
to murder Ding Da.

29
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,280
Previously,

30
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,240
Ding Da was frightened

31
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,159
by the matter of the ghosts.

32
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,919
Fearing he would be the killer's next target,

33
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,240
he decided to hide in

34
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,280
an unexpected place

35
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,080
where no one could find him.

36
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:10,400
So he took a desperate risk

37
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,199
and followed Siniang into the room.

38
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,399
While Siniang wasn't looking,

39
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,639
he hid inside the wardrobe.

40
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,319
Why does it smell like soil?

41
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,560
That is why there is soil in the wardrobe.

42
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:42,279
You mean he stayed in my room all night?

43
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,079
At the Hour of Mao, Siniang locked the door and left.

44
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:54,399
Ding Da then came out of the wardrobe.

45
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,160
Give me back my life!

46
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:06,319
You killed me!

47
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,319
It wasn't me!

48
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:09,720
Give me back my life!

49
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,000
It wasn't me! It wasn't me!

50
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:17,879
Murderer!

51
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,519
You killed me!

52
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,279
It wasn't me!

53
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,600
It wasn't me!

54
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:33,720
It wasn't me!

55
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,000
Give me back my life!

56
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:35,639
It wasn't me!

57
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,839
Give me back my life!

58
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,879
Because the room was damp and cold,

59
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:42,759
Siniang lit a charcoal fire before leaving.

60
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,639
The room was airtight.

61
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,439
Ding Da soon fainted.

62
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,439
A Liang Xiong,

63
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,160
help me out.

64
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,399
Master Kun.

65
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,120
Ready.

66
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:27,560
What is the meaning of this?

67
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,360
Don't rush.

68
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:44,240
Ding Da was already overcome by the charcoal fumes,

69
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:47,480
coupled with these sheets of wet paper,

70
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:51,399
he would slowly suffocate to death in his sleep.

71
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:58,519
After the deed, one just pulls the fine thread

72
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,519
and puts the roof tiles back in place.

73
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,839
It would be done unknowingly,

74
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:05,000
completing a murder within a locked room.

75
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,879
Are you done talking?

76
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,120
I'm getting up now.

77
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,040
But...

78
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,399
when we found Ding Da's body,

79
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:19,920
there were no papers on his face.

80
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,879
That's right.

81
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,199
Wasn't he locked in the room the whole time?

82
00:07:24,199 --> 00:07:24,959
He never went out.

83
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,279
Then that is another trick entirely.

84
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,879
The only one capable of doing this

85
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:34,079
is a single person.

86
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,360
Young Lord.

87
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,160
Young Lord, you personally locked Ding Da in the room last night

88
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,839
and posted heavy guards.

89
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:54,639
If Ding Da tried to escape,

90
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,199
how could you be completely unaware?

91
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:59,680
You saw Ding Da follow Siniang into the room

92
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,480
and decided to strike that night.

93
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,560
You killed Ding Da using water torture.

94
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,560
You needed a witness to clear yourself of suspicion.

95
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,959
Thus, you had to accompany Siniang back to the room.

96
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,680
To make her your locked-room witness.

97
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,199
When the door opened,

98
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,240
Siniang only saw the body from a distance.

99
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,000
You immediately held Siniang back.

100
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,879
And quickly told her to call everyone over.

101
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,320
"I'll keep watch here."

102
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,360
"You go call everyone, quick."

103
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:37,919
"Go, hurry."

104
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:38,399
"Then you stay here, don't move."

105
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,360
"I'll be right back."

106
00:08:51,519 --> 00:08:52,519
After Siniang left,

107
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,320
You entered the room,

108
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,879
And threw the soaked paper from the face into the brazier.

109
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:57,879
That is also why, when we entered the room,

110
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,960
we found that the table leg next to the brazier

111
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,320
had moisture on it.

112
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:26,039
Yu'er was sold by All-Knowing Manor to Master Liu.

113
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,519
So you had to take a desperate risk.

114
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,360
It was to avenge Yu'er, right?

115
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,519
Huang Cui.

116
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,559
They deserved to die.

117
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,759
Our parents died early.

118
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,279
I only had this one brother.

119
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:57,200
The day he went missing was my birthday.

120
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,080
He said he was going to work at the docks,

121
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:01,759
To buy me a birthday cake.

122
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,840
But he never came back.

123
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,600
I had nowhere to go.

124
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,440
I gritted my teeth,

125
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:18,039
I gave myself to the local tyrant of West Street.

126
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:20,720
From him, I learned that

127
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:24,519
Ding Da captured many refugees for All-Knowing Manor.

128
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,039
And Yu'er was there.

129
00:10:27,799 --> 00:10:29,320
I held onto a sliver of hope,

130
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:32,759
Thinking they only took Yu'er to the Manor for hard labor.

131
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,679
As long as I could enter the Manor,

132
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,000
I would be able to find my brother.

133
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,240
So,

134
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,320
I forged an identity,

135
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:45,039
Met the Manor Lord,

136
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,759
And begged him to take me in.

137
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:50,440
I soon gained the Manor Lord's trust.

138
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,200
Step by step, from a common maidservant,

139
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,039
I became the Steward of the Manor.

140
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,200
But I never imagined...

141
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:01,600
Yu'er...

142
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,000
That night,

143
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:11,120
I lured the Manor Lord out.

144
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,639
"Come out here!"

145
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,279
I attacked him when he was off guard.

146
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:19,879
Three stabs.

147
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,480
Sent him to see the King of Hell.

148
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,399
Where is the Manor Lord's head?

149
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,639
Threw it away.

150
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,000
Tossed it.

151
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,519
Fed it to the dogs.
